	</value>
    </Operation>
		<Operation Class="PatchOperationReplace">
		<xpath>Defs/ThingDef[defName="Bamboo"]/description</xpath>
		<value>
			<description>>>> Optimal	Economy
>> Suitible	Beds, Strength
X Inadvisable	Hospitals, Firewood

Sustainability: Uncommon, but very sustainable.

Bamboo is a type of grass that can be made into a composite material that is stronger than many hardwoods.</description>
		</value>
